  "text": "The l α norm with α < 1 is now well-understood to be a natural measure of sparsity [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Of course, this is why [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] approximate the Hamming norm with the l α norm using small α. [CITATION_5] adopted the similar idea to approximate the max-dominance norm in data streams using very small α.",
